node.text:
{ Foreseeing the Future }
.
I went back to the place where I joined to my first instameet, this area has been announced by the government for plans of redevelopment.  I have seen from other friends feeds and knowing many residencies have been taken down.
.
I’ve prepared what I’m going to see around the area, but witnessing at the spot and seeing the emptiness of the area, all the memory flashbacks and THAT feeling still hurt me right into my stomach.  Finding this senior passed me quickly and walked to the never ending empty road, it’s really stabbing me hard. #beinghongkong :: #shotoniphone14pro
